config: cfg.streamPreviewRaw
env: DISCOCLAW_STREAM_PREVIEW_RAW
default: 0 (compact)

objective:
- Make "Thinking..." previews feel live earlier and throughout runtime activity.
- Reduce stale-looking preview blocks without leaking action payloads.

behavior:
- 0 (compact): 8-line tail, 72-char width, compact runtime signal formatting.
- 1 (raw): 14-line tail, 120-char width, richer runtime signal formatting.
- Preview text remains sanitized in both modes; <discord-action> tags (including partial trailing tags) are stripped before rendering.

notes:
- Use `1` when you want denser, continuously changing preview context during long tool-heavy runs.
